snippet.title: Depraved | 1.0 Steam Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Depraved has left the early access program!
Depraved 1.0 is now on Steam with a new trailer!

Depraved is a city builder game with survival aspects, settled in the Wild West. Build towns and establish important outposts to supply your residents with food and other raw materials. Resist the seasons, dangerous animals, and bandits and conquer the Wild West.


More infos at:
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/762650/Depraved
Twitter: https://twitter.com/evilbitegames
